@14   = ~The preparations of the journey have been made and you set out for the Icewind Dale. The road leads you to the city of Baldur?s Gate and the journey continues by sea. After a week of salty waters and pirates you dock on the harbor of Luskan. You stop for awhile to replenish your supplies and then continue the journey to the dalelands. Finally, after weeks of travelling, you arrive to the village of Bremen. It seems that a battle has been fought there just recently and the docks have been wrecked. Only one ship is in order.~
