@156  = ~  When asked about her past, Alissa is quiet first, thinking, and then begins her tale. She was born in a temple devoted for the god Deneir, child to a priest couple. The ways of Deneir were taught to her already when she was very young and she lived quite happily under the priests' guidance. She absorbed their wisdom and to their delight she appeared to be a very lively person. She was quick to learn and was able to use her magical gifts well. But around the age of sixteen she began to learn strange magical abilities on her own. She was confused and did not know the origin of her skills. As she was afraid of them, afraid of what they might mean, she never told anyone about them, not even her parents.
  To the disappointment of the priests, she left the temple at the age of twenty. She wanted to see the world and more secretly, wanted to learn something about her abilites. She has studied books and spoken with a few priests but has found no information concerning such skills. Being afraid of them, she desperately wants to know more about them.~
