@333  = ~  Catti-Brie lost her parents in an attack of a thief group when she was a child, but was rescued by Bruenor Battlehammer, a dwarf leader.
  Bruenor took her as his adoptive daughter and when he forced Wulfgar to serve him for five years, Catti-Brie met her future lover.
  Later on she met the dark elf Drizzt Do'Urden and the halfling Regis.
  Wulfgar and Catti-Brie were happy together and after many adventures they were supposed to get married. But something very unfortunate happened. Wulfgar was lost in a battle and thought as dead.Actually he had been drawn to hell where the demon Errtu tortured him for six long years.
  When Wulfgar was freed he tried to get back what he had had with Catti-Brie. It all ended to Wulfgar hitting her and leaving the party. That was when Catti-Brie and Drizzt started to become closer and closer. Later when Wulfgar had faced the pains of past and returned to everyone's surprise with a wife and a child it didn't affect on the very special relationship Catti-Brie had developed with the dark elf ranger, Drizzt Do'Urden.
  Catti-Brie is known in the world for her beauty and her skills with the magical bow, Taulmaril the Heartseeker. With it, people say, she never misses the target. She is also becoming a skilled sword handler under the guidance of Drizzt Do'Urden who also taught her the ways of the goddess Mielikki and led her into ranger hood.~
