@401  = ~  Drizzt Do'Urden is probably the best drow fighter ever. He was born in the drow city of Menzoberranzan but it never truly became his home. And that is because the drows are cruel people, evil from within. Drizzt is not. His only support in the city was his father Zaknafein.
  Well, Drizzt had no choise but to be persistent in the middle of all kinds of horrors and cruelties and train fighting with scimitars. He became somewhat respected for his skills, but when the matriarch mother of room Do'Urden killed Zaknafein, he had had enough of drows. He escaped to the dangerous and endless caverns of Underdark and fought his way out of there to the upper world.
  Drows are a hated race so Drizzt had a hard time below the sun. At first everybody was hostile but he was able to find some friends like Monitolio who teached him to be a ranger of the goddess Mielikki and Bruenor who gave him a place to stay. A home.
  Later he met Regis, Wulfgar and Catti-Brie. The five of them (Bruenor, Regis, Drizzt, Wulfgar and Catti-Brie) freed the Icewind Dale from Crystal Shard, got the Mithril Hall back to the dwarves and did many other heroic acts.
  When Wulfgar was lost in a battle and thought as dead, Drizzt and Catti-Brie became close. Six years passed and when Drizzt was helping to hunt pirates on a ship he got to understand that his father was still alive and being tortured in hells by powerful demons.
  He set off with his companions on a quest to free his father and was able to bring someone back. It was not his father though. It was Wulfgar who had been tortured for all these years and when he returned everyone was happy, but the situation was pretty awkward. Catti-Brie had been Wulfgar's lover. They tried to get back what they had once had, but with no succees. Wulfgar left the companions and Drizzt and Catti-Brie started to became closer and closer. When Wulfgar was one with himself he finally returned to stay. He had a wife and a child and he accepted the relationship of Drizzt and Catti-Brie.
  Drizzt owns statue of panther. With it he can summon his panther friend Guenhwyvar to fight by his side. Guenhwyvar is Drizzt's most loyal friend and no matter what they are facing, they help each other.~
