@445  = ~  Artemis Entreri is one of the best human fighters. He grew up on the streets of Calimport and got his training there. He was a respected and feared assassin. Succeeded always and never felt sorry for his victims.
  He got to know Bruenor, Regis, Drizzt, Catti-Brie and Wulfgar when he was sent to capture Regis for stealing an amulet from Pasha Pook. He got Regis, sent him back to the Pasha and then made an illusion on himself to look like Regis.
  Drizzt and the others thought Entreri was the real Regis and traveled with him to the Mithril Hall. There the true Entreri was revealed and he battled with Drizzt for the first time.
  After that battle, Drizzt became his obsession. He has battled with Drizzt many times, but never the battles have ended to the death of another one of them.
  When Entreri went to the drow city of Menzoberranzan, he met Jarlaxle. They became companions and Jarlaxle got the Crystal Shard. The two of them lured Drizzt into a Crystal Tower and there Entreri and Drizzt battled for the last time. Entreri thought Drizzt died and his obsession was over....
  But Drizzt didn't die. Jarlaxle had cheated Entreri to think that that was what had happened while actually he had let Drizzt to leave in peace.
  Later Entreri noticed that the Crystal Shard had got a hold on Jarlaxle. He had started to bring drows to Calimport and there was somekind of invasion at hands. Entreri made a plan to steal the Crystal Shard and succeeded in it. At the same time Jarlaxle was betrayed by his lieutenants and he and Entreri had to escape with the Crystal Shard. Entreri insisted that the Shard must be destroyed and together they took it to the priest Cadderly who helped them in destroying it.
  Then the two of them started to travel around the world and after awhile, they found something...~
