@598  = ~  Jarlaxle is the former leader of the thieving commun, Bregan Da'erthe, working in the drow city of Menzoberranzan. He was the most respected male among the drows. Everyone in the Underdark knew him. He is quite a character and can never be seen angry. He is evil, yes, but from cruelty he cannot be blamed.
  One day a human, Artemis Enteri, came to him and some time later he got a powerful object, Crystal Shard. He created a Crystal Tower and lured Drizzt in. There Enteri battled Drizzt for the last time and thought he killed him. But no, Jarlaxle had saved Drizzt without Enteri knowing it.
  But that wasn't the end of Jarlaxle's story. Even a strong minded person like him can be lured by the Crystal Shard's promises of power and strength. He started to bring drows to the upper world and there was somekind of invasion at hands. He was then betrayed by his own and had to flee from the Crystal Tower with Artemis Enteri and the Crystal Shard.
  Enteri was immune to the Crystal Shard and the item in his hands, they were able to bring it to the priest Cadderly who helped them in destroying it. After that they started traveling around the world together, until one day, they found something...~
