@944  = ~Improved Invisibility 10' Radius~
@945  = ~Improved Invisibility 10' radius (Illusion/Phantasm) 
Level: 5
Range: 0
Duration: Special 
Casting Time: 1 round
Area of Effect: 10' radius
Saving Throw: None 

This spell causes all creatures within 10' of the caster to vanish from sight and be undetectable by normal vision or even infravision. The spell remains in effect until it is magically broken or dispelled or until the wizard or recipient cancels it. The invisible being(s) cannot open doors, talk, eat, climb stairs, etc. Note, however, that there are sometimes telltale traces, a shimmering, so that an observant opponent can attack the invisible spell recipient. These traces are only noticeable when specifically looked for (after the invisible character has made his presence known). Attacks against the invisible character suffer -4 penalties to the attack rolls, and the invisible character's saving throws are made with a +4 bonus.~
