@1664 = ~priest of Deneir~
@1665 = ~Priest of Deneir~
@1666 = ~PRIEST OF DENEIR: Deneir is the neutral god of wisdom and illusions. His servants can cast some illusion spells and can evade magical attacks with more success than other priests.

Advantages:
-  Can use Invisibility, Improved Invisibility and Invisibility 10' Radius
